title: Edison Chen - *Complete*
description:
He should never have taken pictures of them. 
He should never have brought that laptop to a stranger.
Oh well.

Let this be a lesson to all, never to do this at home on camera, but at home is fine.


Chen was caught in a sex scandal in January 2008 when hundreds of racy photographs of several high profile female celebrities from the Hong Kong entertainment industry, with whom he had had affairs, were reportedly stolen from his laptop while it had been put in for repair, and numerous images uploaded to the internet. Those celebrities include Gillian Chung, Bobo Chan and Cecilia Cheung. [8] Also explicit photos of Edison Chen himself are uploaded,
